	<article id="post-3503" class="post-3503 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-european-parliament-2 category-gchq category-intelligence category-isc category-law category-media category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-nsa category-osa category-privacy-2 category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-whistleblowers tag-gchq tag-intelligence-2 tag-isc tag-mi5 tag-mi6 tag-nsa tag-oversight tag-snowden tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2 tag-whistleblowers-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/12/recent-interview-voice-russia-spies-democracy-whistleblowers.html" title="Permalink to Voice of Russia radio interview about spies, oversight, whistleblowers, and Snowden." rel="bookmark">Voice of Russia radio interview about spies, oversight, whistleblowers, and Snowden.</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/12/recent-interview-voice-russia-spies-democracy-whistleblowers.html" title="14:58" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-12-07T14:58:03+00:00" pubdate>December 7, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
