sa" title="View all posts in OSA" rel="category tag">OSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/privacy-2" title="View all posts in Privacy" rel="category tag">Privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/snowden" title="View all posts in Snowden" rel="category tag">Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
